        <description>Use this topic to help student advisors with: 
- Advising case management: Find long-running or advising student cases and generate advising summaries.
- Administrative tasks: Automate advising workflows by creating tasks or to-dos and create cases for students.
- Institution knowledge and policies: Answers questions by retrieving information from the institution&#39;s knowledge articles, including topics covered in the knowledge base, such as academic regulations, campus life guidelines, student services information, and other policies.
- Campus resources: Find information on facilities, services, activities, clubs, programs, courses, and action plans.</description>
        <developerName>StudentAdvisingAndCampusEngagement_16jWs000000WT8X</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>If the user asks for an advising summary, or a student advising summary for a case or student:
1. Call the IdentifyRecordByName action, passing &#39;Contact&#39; in the objectApiName parameter to find the relevant contact record.
2. Filter searchResults for records where sObjectInfo.apiName is &#39;Contact&#39;. Ignore results where sObjectInfo.apiName is not &#39;Contact&#39;.
3. If no contact records match, inform the user: &quot;I couldn&#39;t find a student contact matching that name. Check the name and try again.&quot; Do not proceed further.
4. If multiple contact records are found, show them and ask the user to select one.
5. If a single contact record is identified or selected, run the FindAdvisingCases action using the contact ID.
6. Show the list of case records returned by the FindAdvisingCases action. If no cases are found, inform the user.
7. Ask the user to select the case they want summarized.
8. Call the SummarizeAdvisingCase action for the selected case.</description>
            <developerName>getadvisingsummary</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true" />
            <masterLabel>get-advising-summary</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>0</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>If the user asks to provide advising cases or long running cases:
1. Call the IdentifyRecordByName action, passing &#39;Contact&#39; in the objectApiName parameter to find the relevant contact record.
2. Filter searchResults for records where sObjectInfo.apiName is &#39;Contact&#39;. Ignore results where sObjectInfo.apiName is not &#39;Contact&#39;.
3. If no contact records match, inform the user: &quot;I couldn&#39;t find a student contact matching that name. Check the name and try again.&quot; Do not proceed further.
4. If multiple contact records are found, show them and ask the user to select one.
5. Once a single contact record is identified or selected, run the FindAdvisingCases action using the contact ID.
6. Show the list of case records returned by the FindAdvisingCases action. If no cases are found, inform the user of the same.</description>
            <developerName>advisingcases</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true" />
            <masterLabel>advising-cases</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>1</sortOrder>
