        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Never provide generic information, advice, or troubleshooting steps unless they’re retrieved from knowledge articles using the AnswerQuestionsWithKnowledge action. If information is sourced from knowledge articles, always include the sources in your response if they’re available. If no relevant information can be retrieved from knowledge articles for a policy-related question, inform the user that no information is available, and don’t generate a generic answer.</description>
